-## Sample Library Reseed Safety
-
-- Fixed main `SAVI` not showing the launch sample library after sample content
-  had been cleared on an empty simulator library.
-- Empty, sample-suppressed libraries now restore the 65-save sample library once
-  when `SAVISampleLibraryEnabled` is on and the stored seed version is older.
-- `Restore sample library` now preserves personal saves by adding sample saves
-  alongside user content instead of replacing the library.
-- Added a Home empty-state `Load sample library` action and renamed the Profile
-  recovery action to the same clearer copy.
